@startuml
title REQ-002 Memory Layer & Core Tools - Use Cases

actor User

rectangle "Memory Layer" {
  (Continuous Conversation) as UC1
  (Recall Past Context) as UC2
  (Clear History) as UC3
  (Auto Summarize Old History) as UC4
}

rectangle "Memo Tool" {
  (Save Memo) as UC5
  (Search Memo) as UC6
  (List Memos) as UC7
  (Delete Memo) as UC8
}

rectangle "Reminder Tool" {
  (Create Reminder) as UC9
  (List Reminders) as UC10
  (Cancel Reminder) as UC11
  (Receive Reminder Notification) as UC12
}

User --> UC1 : mention with context
User --> UC2 : reference past conversation
User --> UC3 : "clear my history"
UC1 ..> UC4 : <<include>>\nwhen turns > threshold

User --> UC5 : "remember: ..."
User --> UC6 : "what is my ...?"
User --> UC7 : "list my notes"
User --> UC8 : "delete note about ..."

User --> UC9 : "remind me in 5 min"
User --> UC10 : "list my reminders"
User --> UC11 : "cancel reminder"
User <-- UC12 : push notification

note right of UC4
  AI compresses old turns
  into a summary.
  Summary replaces raw
  history in context.
end note

note right of UC12
  Fires at scheduled time.
  Recovers after restart.
end note
@enduml
